snippet.title: Guilty Gear X2 The Midnight Carnival Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the trailer for GGX2 Midnight Carnival, the game that precedent Accent Core and Slash.  It was on the official Sammy site and showed all over Gamefaqs for advertisement in '03.  I looked all over and couldn't find it on youtube, I hope you all enjoy for those who even remember this.

I don't own this video, it belongs to Sammy/Sega and Daisuke Ishiwatari.  

Note:  It contains the Opening music of the game and Still in the Dark.
